vaanam ( english : fire ) is a 1988 indian tamil film directed by radhakrishna jagarlamudi and produced by s. a. chandrasekhar . the film features an ensemble cast consisting of yuvan shankar raja , the film is about the life of the elder brother . the film was released on 30 april 2011 . the film was remade in tamil as vaanam &lt;unk&gt; .